**Step 1**: Open the `build.gradle` file of your project.

**Step 2**: Make sure that the repositories section includes a `maven` section with the [https://maven.google.com][1] `url` in it.

    allprojects {
        repositories {
            google() // here
            jcenter()
            maven { url &#39;https://maven.google.com&#39; }
        }
    }


  [1]: https://maven.google.com

